    <Note Title="Topic" Type="Summary" Ordinal="1" xml:lang="en">Security update for bind</Note>
    <Note Title="Details" Type="General" Ordinal="2" xml:lang="en">
BIND was updated to fix a denial of service against servers performing
validation on DNSSEC-signed records (CVE-2015-5722, bsc#944066).
</Note>
